{"tid":2351842,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下翻part time請一日病假就比人炒係咪可以穩勞工處","createTime":"2021-01-03T14:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:49:51.000Z","uid":386264,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d2272aab2f393428fa1eb68b785ab0402f6f3e2e","tid":2351842,"uid":386264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小妹翻開part time間公司一路以黎都唔係好夠人用 好多時候間公司都強行比更逼我翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁去到最近因為天氣太凍真係病o左(有病假紙)，於是乎我早幾日就同個manager講我真係病o左翻唔到工啦， 點知佢都係比更我，最後果日我因為病左翻唔到工<br />\n<br />\n夜晚黑就比個manager wts寸我+炒我 宜家條氣好唔撚順 想問下係咪有方法煩到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461e3f58e42cf1f3522ae27994d7489b35015817","tid":2351842,"uid":375706,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"依加咁既時勢病都仲想你番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d92a44191c1dea129c68f60b99173fcccb6010c","tid":2351842,"uid":9683,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"你預知幾日後會病？？"},{"pid":"08d2ebf93e6c5a0e5c4ec57cca30eb3ab149a167","tid":2351842,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"買起佢全家算啦"},{"pid":"de88496afa69a8a5c03f1023fd9f8e4bb0f04b20","tid":2351842,"uid":35031,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5d92a44191c1dea129c68f60b99173fcccb6010c","tid":2351842,"uid":9683,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"你預知幾日後會病？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"病幾日好出奇咩<br />\n話說pt就算啦<br />\n如果要認真既咪睇下佢符唔符合418連續性合約<br />\n符合既佢炒你都係要有通知期<br />\n但你阻唔到佢炒你囉"},{"pid":"eca213af0f61d3d8ab22ebab970060fe7bbcb125","tid":2351842,"uid":131264,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyT